Phase 1: Create Solution

Create folder:

DoctorAppointmentSystem

Open terminal:

dotnet new sln -n DoctorAppointmentSystem
Phase 2: Create Projects

Create API:

dotnet new webapi -n DoctorAppointment.API

Create Application:

dotnet new classlib -n DoctorAppointment.Application

Create Domain:

dotnet new classlib -n DoctorAppointment.Domain

Create Infrastructure:

dotnet new classlib -n DoctorAppointment.Infrastructure

Create Persistence:

dotnet new classlib -n DoctorAppointment.Persistence
